race.description: Mt Misery Sand & Soil Maiden Plate
race.comment: EDEN ROSE (8) has placed in town and should be winning in this company. Just missed at Kilmore two back and will find this miles easier than Sandown last time. Has won a jumpout since and has the inside gate. There certainly is a lot to like. SHAY'S WAY (7) returns from a layoff and she filled a minor placing first-up last time in work over 1400m at Ballarat Synthetic. Looks the biggest hurdle in the path of EDEN ROSE. MESSAGE BANK (6) debuts and looked good placing in her latest jumpout. Profiles well and deserves a betting watch. ANALYTICAL (1) has room for further improvement and can be the pick of the rest.
